{"itemid":1220,"subject":"Coming Next Month","event":"Coming in March... a new TV tie-in edition of A GAME OF THRONES for season three.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://grrm.livejournal.com/pics/catalog/460/158759\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://ic.pics.livejournal.com/grrm/7059164/158759/158759_300.jpg\" alt=\"Game 2013 MTI trade\" title=\"Game 2013 MTI trade\" width=\"198\" height=\"300\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe new cover will be available on both mass market and trade paperback formats, I believe.  Maybe on a hardcover reprint as well, though I am less sure of that.  When I know for certain, I will pass along the info here.\r\n\r\nFURTHER INFO.  Ok, got a clarification.  This new artwork will appear on the paperbacks, both mass market and trade.  The hardcover will retain its present cover.  Also, a repackage of A STORM OF SWORDS is also in the works, and will feature key art from the HBO series.  I will post that here when it's ready.","ditemid":312483,"eventtime":"2013-02-13 14:05:00","props":{"current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"a song of ice and fire, game of thrones","current_moodid":109,"commentalter":1361213790,"opt_lockcomments":1,"picture_keyword":"Spain","opt_screening":"F","personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","revnum":2,"interface":"web","revtime":1361727243},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2013-02-13 21:05:18","anum":163,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html","event_timestamp":1360764300,"reply_count":17,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/120124537/60379360","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17262499#t17262499","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17262499#t17262499","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17262499#t17262499","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_1649870","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://t