at goes into fashioning them.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"February 14 2013, 04:20:21 UTC","parent":17266339,"massactions":0,"subject":"Re: Cover art","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/jwmather","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Jim Mather","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_1650010","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=60381262&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Jim Mather","ctime_ts":1360815621,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17265827#t17265827","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17265827#t17265827","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17265827#t17265827","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_1650030","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://profiles.google.com/103869058528529182598","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":17265827,"talkid":67444,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/312483.html?thread=17265827#t17265827","upictitle":"ext_1650030: pic#0","article":"I always hated reading. Until Game Of Thrones came by.<br />I'm 12 years old, and used to always love reading comic books and loathed novels. Until i Game Of Thrones peaked my interest.<br /><br />I began to read Game Of Thrones, and i surprisingly loved it despite my past experiences. I was awfully engaged into it, reading page by page and word by word. I continued into Clash Of Kings, Storm Of Swords, Feast For Crows and then a Dance With Dragons.<br /><br />Game Of Thrones began my reading spree. I started reading books and books, 